    <briefdescription>
<para>Field lookup output for current or fallback equality-delete fields. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><computeroutput>field</computeroutput> is the exact field for validation. <computeroutput>projection_field</computeroutput> is the top-level field, possibly with a pruned nested struct path, that must be merged into RequiredSchema so the data reader can materialize the delete column. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
